{"tid":484632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook收一個讚挨一拳！ 妙齡妻慘遭妒夫打到面目全非","createTime":"2017-11-30T09:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T10:11:58.000Z","uid":75969,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"10e6d90b0a336e2dc64ad0f8dd4923448cd5083e","tid":484632,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕巴拉圭一名21歲人妻奧媞芶札（Adolfina Camelli Ortigoza），只要個人臉書照片有人按讚，32歲丈夫賈勒亞諾（Pedro Heriberto Galeano）就會打翻醋罈子動手，一個讚就打一次，害她整張臉腫成豬頭，嘴破齒斷。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，賈勒亞諾似乎疑心病很重，一見有人按妻子臉書讚或留言，就會瞬間抓狂，認為兩人「有染」，痛毆奧媞芶札洩憤，更駭人的是，<span style=\"color: red;\">賈勒亞諾還逼迫妻子交出帳號密碼，假藉其名義繼續貼照發文，獲讚後又拳打腳踢</span>，導致妻子全身上下傷痕累累，甚至一聽到電子載具傳來通知用戶有新訊息的「叮咚」聲，就會不自覺顫抖。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，賈勒亞諾怕鄰居聽見妻子的哀嚎聲，施虐前還特地拿塊布塞進對方嘴裡，並長期監禁她，讓她無法向外求援。所幸賈父得知後，「大義滅親」趕緊報警處理，成功救出乖媳婦，可惜原本清純可人的女子，如今卻被「毀容」，醜到連自己照鏡子都認不出來，未來還得進行臉部重建手術。事後賈勒亞諾被依謀殺、剝奪人身自由等罪起訴，一旦罪刑確定，恐面臨30年有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2269160\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2269160&d=rPrMM9fTeMIE5kslOftNdTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=6bc93b2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2269160&h=b39370b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2269160</a>"},{"pid":"48158a853f1c60b00aa8064318ac497d2009e621","tid":484632,"uid":75969,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T09:06:59.000Z","msg":"0個like<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpEfxwqk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpEfxwqk.jpg&h=e2f42731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n100個like<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpymcarf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.c